      <h3>Eyes of the Machine: Computer Vision in Post-Harvest Quality</h3>
      <p>A deep dive into automating quality control for agrifood produce. How non-destructive AI sensing ensures shelf-life, reduces waste, and standardizes global trade.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="topic-card">
