          <h3>The First Leaf: AI & Computer Vision in Forestry Nurseries</h3>
          <p>Transforming silviculture through automated seedling QC. How AI monitors viability and stress in the nursery to ensure higher survival rates, better timber quality, and more resilient reforestation at scale.</p>
    </div>

